{"parentUuid":"ee70d481-0cf0-4f86-9f1d-b0b0317fd641","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"bbc5f1a8-c98d-42a9-81b2-366ab479d0fc","version":"2.1.63","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"content":[{"thinking":"用户问\"SVG插图是什么\"，这是一个关于SVG（可缩放矢量图形）的基础概念问题。我应该简洁地解释SVG插图的含义和特点。\n\n根据我的指令，我应该：\n- 简洁直接地回答\n- 不使用emoji（除非用户明确要求）\n- 使用技术性但易懂的语言\n\n我注意到系统提示中提到了一个技能\"svg-article-illustrator\"，但用户只是在问概念，不是要使用这个技能，所以我不需要调用它。\n","type":"thinking","signature":""}],"id":"msg_c61a730ffaeb4458b52d816dd64c059a","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":29545,"output_tokens":1}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"2c313382-8a5b-4654-95ab-c613c8789821","timestamp":"2026-03-01T10:49:44.852Z"}
{"parentUuid":"2c313382-8a5b-4654-95ab-c613c8789821","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"bbc5f1a8-c98d-42a9-81b2-366ab479d0fc","version":"2.1.63","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"content":[{"text":"SVG插图是使用SVG（Scalable Vector Graphics，可缩放矢量图形）格式创建的图像。\n\n主要特点：\n\n- **矢量格式**：基于数学公式而非像素，可以无限放大缩小而不失真\n- **文本格式**：本质是XML代码，可以用文本编辑器直接编辑\n- **体积小**：相比位图（PNG/JPG）文件更小，适合网页使用\n- **可编程**：可以用CSS和JavaScript动态控制样式和动画\n- **清晰度高**：在任何分辨率的屏幕上都保持清晰\n\n常见用途：\n- 网站图标和Logo\n- 数据可视化图表\n- 技术文档配图\n- 响应式网页插图\n- 动态交互图形\n\n相比传统位图（PNG/JPG），SVG更适合需要缩放、动画或程序化生成的场景。","type":"text"}],"id":"msg_c61a730ffaeb4458b52d816dd64c059a","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":32504,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":344,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"f4be3a16-8ea4-4806-9070-74735ff5742b","timestamp":"2026-03-01T10:49:48.445Z"}
